Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:46.92,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,Holding on, even to our pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:53.71,ED JP 12-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,360)\bord0\fax-0.1}新しい景色　迎えに行こう
