Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:13.28,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,yuuhi ni kazashita yubisaki
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:13.28,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,I shaded myself from the setting sun,
