Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.37,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,The prism of my fingertips reflected orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:29.32,ED JP 12-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\bord0\fax-0.1}自分のすべてを許せるくらいに
